OL,3,CFresh call for flu jab uptake as cases
OL,4,Crise amid health board's face-mask rule
OL,6,FWales' Chief Medical Officer has
OL,7,Frenewed calls for people to get their
OL,8,Fflu vaccine as cases spike across the
OL,9,Fcountry.
OL,11,FProfessor Isabel Oliver said
OL,12,Fpreventable deaths occur every year.
OL,14,FShe said: "It is really important that
OL,15,Feveryone who has been invited to have
OL,16,Fthe vaccine, everyone who is eligible,
OL,17,Feither because of their age or because
OL,18,Fthey have health conditions takes up
OL,19,Fthe offer of (the) vaccine...
