OL,3,CFresh call for flu jab uptake as cases
OL,4,Crise amid health board's face-mask rule
OL,6,F"It is also important that we take
OL,7,Fprecautions if we are unwell because
OL,8,Fof respiratory illness to prevent the
OL,9,Fspread onto other people, for example
OL,10,Fusing masks."
OL,12,FIt comes after Cwm Taf Morgannwg
OL,13,FUniversity Health Board enforced
OL,14,Fcompulsory mask-wearing for all staff
OL,15,Fand visitors across its hospital sites
OL,16,Fearlier this week following a
OL,17,F"significant rise" in flu cases. Those
OL,18,Fmeasures are due to be reviewed on
OL,19,FFriday, 28 November.
