OL,3,CFresh call for flu jab uptake as cases
OL,4,Crise amid health board's face-mask rule
OL,6,FThe health board has also strongly
OL,7,Fencouraged people to only visit
OL,8,Fhospital sites if absolutely necessary
OL,9,Fto reduce the risk of transmission.
OL,11,FPublic Health Wales has reported a
OL,12,Frise in the Influenza A strain, which
OL,13,Fcan cause severe illness, particularly
OL,14,Fin older and vulnerable people.
OL,16,FAlready, more than 700,000 flu
OL,17,Fvaccines have been delivered across
OL,18,FWales.
