OL,3,CFresh call for flu jab uptake as cases
OL,4,Crise amid health board's face-mask rule
OL,6,FDr Christopher Johnson, head of the
OL,7,FVaccine Preventable Disease Programme,
OL,8,Fstressed the need for renewed
OL,9,Fprotection, saying: "Protection from
OL,10,Fprevious vaccines fades over time. The
OL,11,Fflu vaccine is updated every year to
OL,12,Fmatch circulating strains and give
OL,13,Fpeople the best protection.
OL,14,FVaccination is one of the most
OL,15,Feffective tools we have, it's quick,
OL,16,Fsafe and gives protection within 14
OL,17,Fdays."
